# line-string-unicode

## Input

```
a Hello 😀🎉
b 日本語テスト
c café résumé

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..55
  ENTRY@0..17
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    LINE_STRING@2..16
      STRING@2..16 "Hello 😀🎉"
    NEWLINE@16..17 "\n"
  ENTRY@17..38
    WORD_KEY@17..18
      WORD@17..18 "b"
    SPACE@18..19 " "
    LINE_STRING@19..37
      STRING@19..37 "日本語テスト"
    NEWLINE@37..38 "\n"
  ENTRY@38..55
    WORD_KEY@38..39
      WORD@38..39 "c"
    SPACE@39..40 " "
    LINE_STRING@40..54
      STRING@40..54 "café résumé"
    NEWLINE@54..55 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@2..16 "Hello 😀🎉",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@17..18 "b",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@19..37 "日本語テスト",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@38..39 "c",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@40..54 "café résumé",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

